\n{{col-end}}\n\nOn 23 October 2008 [[FC Zvezda Irkutsk]] had to stop participation in the league due to lack of funds, their main sponsor [[Interavia Airlines|Interavia]] airlines is having financial problems at the time.<ref>[http://www.vesti.ru/doc.html?id=218200&cid=7&t_only=1 Interavia lets Irkutsk footballers down]</ref> Zvezda failed to fulfil four last fixtures.\n\n==Standings==\n\n<onlyinclude>{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|show_limit=5\n|res_col_header=PR\n\n|team1=ROS|name_ROS=[[FC Rostov|Rostov]]\n|team2=KUB|name_KUB=[[FC Kuban Krasnodar|Kuban Krasnodar]]\n|team3=KAM|name_KAM=[[FC KAMAZ Naberezhnye Chelny|KAMAZ Naberezhnye Chelny]]\n|team4=URL|name_URL=[[FC Ural Sverdlovsk Oblast|Ural Sverdlovsk Oblast]]\n|team5=NOS|name_NOS=[[FC Nosta Novotroitsk|Nosta Novotroitsk]]\n|team6=ANZ|name_ANZ=[[FC Anzhi Makhachkala|Anzhi Makhachkala]]\n|team7=BAL|name_BAL=[[FC Baltika Kaliningrad|Baltika Kaliningrad]]\n|team8=SKE|name_SKE=[[FC SKA-Khabarovsk|SKA-Khabarovsk]]\n|team9=CHE|name_CHE=[[FC Chernomorets Novorossiysk|Chernomorets Novorossiysk]]\n|team10=ALA|name_ALA=[[FC Alania Vladikavkaz|Alania Vladikavkaz]]\n|team11=VIT|name_VIT=[[FC Vityaz Podolsk|Vityaz Podolsk]]\n|team12=SAE|name_SAE=[[FC Salyut-Energia Belgorod|Salyut-Energia Belgorod]]\n|team13=SKA|name_SKA=[[FC SKA Rostov-on-Don|SKA Rostov-on-Don]]\n|team14=SIB|name_SIB=[[FC Sibir Novosibirsk|Sibir Novosibirsk]]\n|team15=SAK|name_SAK=[[FC Sportakademklub Moscow|Sportakademklub Moscow]]\n|team16=MTK|name_MTK=[[FC Metallurg-Kuzbass Novokuznetsk|Metallurg-Kuzbass Novokuznetsk]]\n|team17=VOL|name_VOL=[[FC Volga Ulyanovsk|Volga Ulyanovsk]]\n|team18=TOR|name_TOR=[[FC Torpedo Moscow|Torpedo Moscow]]\n|team19=KMV|name_KMV=[[FC Mashuk-KMV Pyatigorsk|Mashuk-KMV Pyatigorsk]]\n|team20=DBN|name_DBN=[[FC Dynamo Barnaul|Dynamo Barnaul]]\n|team21=DBR|name_DBR=[[FC Dynamo Bryansk|Dynamo Bryansk]]\n|team22=ZVE|name_ZVE=[[FC Zvezda Irkutsk|Zvezda Irkutsk]]\n|win_ROS=29|draw_ROS=9|loss_ROS=4|gf_ROS=78|ga_ROS=29|status_